  m_Name: GameIntro_Data
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::LevelIntroData
  levelTitle: WELCOME, GUARDIAN
  levelContext: 'The balance of nature is under threat.


    Across Canada, ecosystems
    are being disrupted by invasive species, pollution, and human impact. These changes
    ripple through water, wildlife, and entire food webs.


    That''s where you
    come in.


    You''ve been chosen to restore balance, protect vulnerable habitats,
    and stop environmental threats before they spread beyond control. Every decision
    you make will shape the future of these ecosystems.


    Your journey begins
    now.'
